CatDescriptText: Cutline of related images published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 8, 1959, pg. B9 reads: "Frog Week Events Highlight Gay Social Season..."
TitMainTitle: FROGS members, including Morris Fountain Sr., Buddy Leftwich, Wendell Freeland in front, and Percy Garland, Dr. Hale, Bill Frederick, Judge Henry Smith, and Dr. Reginald Dixon in back, posed in Gateway Plaza ballroom for FROGS formal
